### 教师注册
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "teacher001",
  "password": "123456",
  "realName": "王老师",
  "role": "teacher",
  "className": "软件2301班"
}

### 学生注册
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "student001",
  "password": "123456",
  "realName": "张三",
  "role": "student",
  "className": "软件2301班"
}

### 教师登录
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "teacher001",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 学生登录
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "student001",
  "password": "123456"
}